-paragraph-index=3D"0"><div class=3D"paragraph">If we examine the Euclidean=
 Algorithm we can see that it makes use of the following properties:</div><=
/div></div></div><div class=3D"clearfix"><div class=3D"perseus-renderer per=
seus-renderer-responsive"><div class=3D"paragraph" data-perseus-paragraph-i=
ndex=3D"0"><ul><li>GCD(A,0) =3D A</li><li>GCD(0,B) =3D B</li><li><strong>If=
